{"tid":2104364,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"30歲陳穎欣傳曾為愛與隊友反目　《地產仔》女星顏值勝《殺手》？","createTime":"2020-07-12T01:59:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-14T07:50:41.000Z","uid":12558,"like":2,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"eaf26d42260959f867dfe93aa4178ed93dfba42a","tid":2104364,"uid":12558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T01:59:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20200703/355795993352081408.jpeg/YUuYOou3hJYt3y60q2zl_xaJ4XfRAWMqetUxYnrVMWI?v=w1280r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20200703%2F355795993352081408.jpeg%2FYUuYOou3hJYt3y60q2zl_xaJ4XfRAWMqetUxYnrVMWI%3Fv%3Dw1280r16_9&h=2c9e21dc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n由陳穎欣、廖子妤、吳肇軒主演的ViuTv劇集《地產仔》與李佳芯、龔嘉欣、陳豪、黎耀祥主演的TVB劇集《殺手》打對台，雖然卡司相差甚遠，但劇中的影視界新臉孔讓劇集引起不少人討論。女主角陳穎欣（Yanny）是女團Super Girls出身，近年才轉戰電視圈，但際遇不錯，之前在ViuTv劇集《仇老爺爺》擔正做遊學修女友，《地產仔》又再次飾演地產女神，與吳肇軒有感情線。<br />\n<br />\nSuper Girls出道10年　成員愛情路多坎坷?<br />\n<br />\n陳穎欣（Yanny）接連兩劇擔正，隨Super Girls出道10年，終於捱出頭。事業順遂，愛情路也是。Yanny與音樂監製男友陳考威（Gareth）拍拖3年，感情穩定。不過年初Yanny曾到香港開電視節目《開運秘笈》任嘉賓，堪輿學家楊天命批Yanny的真命天子年紀比她小，而且是享樂型肥仔，當時她聞言後更大為緊張，直言「你而家講嘅，全部都不是我男朋友特徵，咁點算好？」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20200703/355750054994251776.jpeg/5bnu0_YRGKT_AHgf6FIkkmv0oWuvWle7aV-ic2lfonM?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20200703%2F355750054994251776.jpeg%2F5bnu0_YRGKT_AHgf6FIkkmv0oWuvWle7aV-ic2lfonM%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=181522bd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n陳穎欣食煙一幕，也引起不少網民討論。（《地產仔》劇照<br />\n<br />\n雖然嘴上這樣說，但兩人不時在Instagram互相留言耍花槍，看來兩人依然恩愛。Yanny收穫美滿愛情，Super Girls其他成員情路大多都波折重重......<br />\n<br />\n李靜儀Heidi-至今單身<br />\n<br />\n提起Super Girls，不少人仍會想起李靜儀（Heidi）與陳穎欣（Yanny）先後Gareth拍拖，當時Yanny與Gareth的緋聞傳出，Heidi立即在Instagram上取消追蹤Yanny，所以傳出兩人反目，當時Yanny被網民圍攻，只是Yanny始終不做解釋，只是說兩人的確因為吵架互相取消追蹤，但之後已經和好如初。不過，至今兩人同場的互動仍會引起大眾關注。Super Girls各自發展後，Heidi曾經「單飛」出新歌，但感情上一直都沒有着落。雖然她多次直言自己渴望愛情，但似乎一直都未能遇上真命天子。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20200703/355751886571311104.jpeg/9onujeSZhxDJS4u2E2zfoCmaS0HtXT-CJsjg3ibI4N4?v=w480\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20200703%2F355751886571311104.jpeg%2F9onujeSZhxDJS4u2E2zfoCmaS0HtXT-CJsjg3ibI4N4%3Fv%3Dw480&h=732ef27f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n吳嘉熙Cheronna-情傷未癒<br />\n<br />\n吳嘉熙（Cheronna）曾經與夏雨兒子黃奕晨（Dixon）拍拖，兩人常常放閃，更在IG上自創「#黃奕晨與吳嘉熙的共同hashtag」，曾經情侶檔上節目，成員都直言Cheronna有望成為Super Girls第二位新娘子。然而，兩人卻在去年尾宣布已經和平分手，Cheronna分手後明顯消瘦不少。她受訪時直言自己感性大於理性，結束上一段感情，心情尚未平復，所以未準備好面對下一段感情。"},{"pid":"73db280370067ed86865616d10c7f5da9bc2fb05","tid":2104364,"uid":127929,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T02:01:34.000Z","msg":"又係情傷系列<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n識親啲女都一定話自己有抑鬱<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2104084\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2104084</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"45cfcb9d7e9a77f11bf4685b5641da2d1ae00b33","tid":2104364,"uid":108606,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T02:02:40.000Z","msg":"見到陳穎欣就會諗起gay廉 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a760128b0c973124d8b930a6a8b68fd38c704c40","tid":2104364,"uid":99700,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T02:05:15.000Z","msg":"老撚到"},{"pid":"66c85788dab26a4db306481d22578ee3725353dd","tid":2104364,"uid":56716,"like":6,"dislike":3,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T02:05:46.000Z","msg":"Heidi同yanny都靚靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3543d6a3be3bc1e91300d4970187195e545d0990","tid":2104364,"uid":52605,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":